      <scopecontent id="aspace_4ba307b3c4770c5f64770dc99a2b5e3e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers include correspondence, lectures and writings, and photographs that date primarily from Paul Beeson's later years. They include honors and tributes from former students and colleagues and attest to the influence Beeson had as a teacher.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
